THIRD-PARTY ROMS AND SOFTWARE NOTICE

This repository includes certain third-party files for emulator compatibility,
testing, and historic preservation. The public domain dedication (The Unlicense)
applies ONLY to the original emulator source code and custom files created for 
this project. It does NOT apply to the following bundled files, which remain the 
property of their respective copyright holders:

1. ROMs (located in the roms/ directory):
   - ACI.rom, basic.rom, WozMonitor.rom: Copyrighted by Apple Computer, Inc.
   - charmap.rom: MCM2513 character generator ROM, copyrighted by Motorola/etc.
   - krusader-1.3.rom: Copyright Ken Wessen.
   - applesoft-lite-*.rom, cffa1.rom, sdcard.rom, jukebox.rom: Various authors.

2. Cassette Tapes & Software (located in cassettes/ and software/ directories):
   - Classic games, demos, utilities, and audio recordings. These are copyrighted
     by their original authors or publishers (e.g., Apple Computer, Inc. for 
     Integer BASIC programs, various creators/composers for SID files and demos).
     They are included here solely for historic preservation, interoperability,
     and emulation testing.
